{"type":"user","uuid":"286a07aa-a47b-4d97-a960-3413b5969384","session_id":"652c262b-723d-40ce-86a3-383fcc2d8e4b","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_23b38d3b53e34d5abbddd2b7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-003: Task Breakdown\n   2→\n   3→## Task Summary\n   4→\n   5→| Phase | Range | Count |\n   6→|-------|-------|-------|\n   7→| Setup | T-001 ~ T-009 | 3 |\n   8→| Foundational | T-010 ~ T-099 | 6 |\n   9→| User Stories | T-100 ~ T-199 | 7 |\n  10→| Polish | T-900 ~ T-999 | 2 |\n  11→\n  12→---\n  13→\n  14→## Setup Phase (T-001 ~ T-009)\n  15→\n  16→### T-001 [P] Create plans directory structure\n  17→\n  18→- [ ] **T-001** [P] Create plans directory structure — file: plans/, .gitignore\n  19→\n  20→**Goal**: 创建版本化计划文件的存储目录结构\n  21→\n  22→**Input**: 项目根路径\n  23→\n  24→**Output**:\n  25→- `plans/` 目录\n  26→- `plans/feature-list/` 目录\n  27→- `plans/bug-fix-list/` 目录\n  28→- `.gitignore` 更新（忽略版本文件，保留 `_current.json`）\n  29→\n  30→**Acceptance**:\n  31→- 目录结构存在且可写\n  32→- `.gitignore` 正确配置\n  33→\n  34→**Complexity**: low\n  35→\n  36→---\n  37→\n  38→### T-002 [P] Install Ajv dependency\n  39→\n  40→- [ ] **T-002** [P] Install Ajv dependency — file: package.json\n  41→\n  42→**Goal**: 安装 JSON Schema 校验库\n  43→\n  44→**Input**: package.json\n  45→\n  46→**Output**:\n  47→- `ajv` 依赖添加到 package.json\n  48→- `npm install` 执行成功\n  49→\n  50→**Acceptance**:\n  51→- `npm ls ajv` 显示正确版本\n  52→- 无安全漏洞警告\n  53→\n  54→**Complexity**: low\n  55→\n  56→---\n  57→\n  58→### T-003 [P] Extend config-loader with plansDir\n  59→\n  60→- [ ] **T-003** [P] Extend config-loader with plansDir — file: src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js\n  61→\n  62→**Goal**: 扩展配置加载器支持计划文件目录\n  63→\n  64→**Input**: config-loader.js\n  65→\n  66→**Output**:\n  67→- 新增 `plansDir` 配置项\n  68→- 默认值：`projectRoot/plans`\n  69→- 支持环境变量 `PLANS_DIR` 覆盖\n  70→\n  71→**Acceptance**:\n  72→- `loadPipelineInfraConfig()` 返回 `plansDir`\n  73→- 测试覆盖新配置项\n  74→\n  75→**Complexity**: 