{"type":"user","uuid":"cbcc1cde-dcee-44da-8185-b276a8f0aac1","session_id":"652c262b-723d-40ce-86a3-383fcc2d8e4b","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde5fe6ea814b4fb4f384213ce08a","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-003: Technical Implementation Plan\n   2→\n   3→## Architecture Overview\n   4→\n   5→```\n   6→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n   7→│                     Telegram Bot Entry                       │\n   8→│                   src/bot/telegram.js                        │\n   9→│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐│\n  10→│  │ Document Handler (new)                                   ││\n  11→│  │ - Listen for document messages                           ││\n  12→│  │ - Filter JSON files                                      ││\n  13→│  │ - Delegate to plan-ingestion-service                     ││\n  14→│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘│\n  15→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  16→                              │\n  17→                              ▼\n  18→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  19→│                   Command Router (F-002)                     │\n  20→│              src/bot/commands/index.js                       │\n  21→│  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐      │\n  22→│  │ /plan        │  │ /plan status │  │ /plan use    │      │\n  23→│  │ handler      │  │ handler      │  │ handler      │      │\n  24→│  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘      │\n  25→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  26→                              │\n  27→                              ▼\n  28→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  29→│                Plan Ingestion Service                        │\n  30→│          src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js              │\n  31→│  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐      │\n  32→│  │ Schema       │  │ Version      │  │ Plan         │      │\n  33→│  │ Validator    │  │ Manager      │  │ Registry     │      │\n  34→│  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘      │\n  35→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  36→                              │\n  37→                              ▼\n  38→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  39→│              Pipeline Control Service (F-001)                │\n  40→│          src/services/pipeline-control-service.js            │\n  41→│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐│\n  42→│  │ - Accepts listPath parameter for dynamic plan switching  ││\n  43→│  │ - Integrates with plan registry for version resolution   ││\n  44→│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘│\n  45→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  46→                              │\n  47→                              ▼\n  48→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  49→│                    File Storage Layer                        │\n  50→│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐│\n  51→│  │ plans/                                                    ││\n  52→│  │ ├── feature-list/                                        ││\n  53→│  │ │   ├── v20260312-143052.json                           ││\n  54→│  │ │   ├── v20260312-160321.json                           ││\n  55→│  │ │   └── _current.json -> v20260312-160321.json          ││\n  56→│  │ └── bug-fix-list/                                        ││\n  57→│  │     ├── v20260312-143100.json                           ││\n  58→│  │     └── _current.json                                    ││\n  59→│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘│\n  60→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  61→```\n  62→\n  63→---\n  64→\n  65→## Component Design\n  66→\n  67→### 1. Plan Validator (`src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js`)\n  68→\n  69→**Purpose**: 验证计划文件是否符合 schema 规范。\n  70→\n  71→**Interface**:\n  72→```typescript\n  73→interface ValidationResult {\n  74→  valid: boolean;\n  75→  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list' | 'unknown';\n  76→  errors: ValidationError[];\n  77→  summary?: PlanSummary;\n  78→}\n  79→\n  80→interface ValidationError {\n  81→  path: string;        // JSON path, e.g., \"features[0].id\"\n  82→  message: string;     // Human-readable error\n  83→  keyword?: string;    // JSON Schema keyword\n  84→}\n  85→\n  86→interface PlanSummary {\n  87→  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list';\n  88→  name: string;        // app_name or project_name\n  89→  itemCount: number;   // features or bugs count\n  90→  statusBreakdown: Record<string, number>;\n  91→}\n  92→\n  93→function validatePlanFile(content: string): ValidationResult;\n  94→```\n  95→\n  96→**Logic**:\n  97→1. 解析 JSON 内容\n  98→2. 识别 `$schema` 字段确定类型\n  99→3. 加载对应 schema 文件（从 dev-pipeline/templates/）\n 100→4. 执行 Ajv 校验\n 101→5. 转换错误信息为用户友好格式\n 102→6. 生成内容摘要\n 103→\n 104→---\n 105→\n 106→### 2. Version Manager (`src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js`)\n 107→\n 108→**Purpose**: 管理计划文件的版本化存储。\n 109→\n 110→**Interface**:\n 111→```typescript\n 112→interface VersionInfo {\n 113→  version: string;      // e.g., \"v20260312-143052\"\n 114→  timestamp: Date;\n 115→  size: number;         // bytes\n 116→  itemCount: number;\n 117→  isValid: boolean;\n 118→}\n 119→\n 120→interface SaveResult {\n 121→  success: boolean;\n 122→  version?: string;\n 123→  error?: string;\n 124→}\n 125→\n 126→function savePlanVersion(\n 127→  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list',\n 128→  content: string,\n 129→  meta: { validatedBy: string }\n 130→): Promise<SaveResult>;\n 131→\n 132→function listVersions(\n 133→  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list'\n 134→): Promise<VersionInfo[]>;\n 135→\n 136→function getVersionContent(\n 137→  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list',\n 138→  version: string\n 139→): Promise<string | null>;\n 140→\n 141→function setCurrentVersion(\n 142→  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list',\n 143→  version: string\n 144→): Promise<boolean>;\n 145→\n 146→function getCurrentVersion(\n 147→  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list'\n 148→): Promise<string | null>;\n 149→\n 150→function rollbackVersion(\n 151→  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list'\n 152→): Promise<{ previousVersion: string; currentVersion: string } | null>;\n 153→```\n 154→\n 155→---\n 156→\n 157→### 3. Plan Registry (`src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js`)\n 158→\n 159→**Purpose**: 维护当前生效版本与元数据。\n 160→\n 161→**Interface**:\n 162→```typescript\n 163→interface PlanRegistry {\n 164→  getActivePath(type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list'): string;\n 165→  getActiveMeta(type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list'): ActiveMeta | null;\n 166→  refresh(): void;\n 167→}\n 168→\n 169→interface ActiveMeta {\n 170→  version: string;\n 171→  path: string;\n 172→  lastModified: Date;\n 173→  itemCount: number;\n 174→}\n 175→```\n 176→\n 177→**Implementation**:\n 178→- 使用 `_current.json` 文件存储当前版本信息\n 179→- 或使用 symlink 指向当前版本文件\n 180→- 提供 `getActivePath()` 供 pipeline-control-service 使用\n 181→\n 182→---\n 183→\n 184→### 4. Command Handlers\n 185→\n 186→#### Plan Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/plan.js`)\n 187→\n 188→```typescript\n 189→interface PlanParams {\n 190→  action: 'status' | 'versions' | 'use' | 'rollback' | 'validate';\n 191→  type?: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list';\n 192→  version?: string;\n 193→}\n 194→\n 195→async function handlePlan(ctx: Context, params: PlanParams): Promise<void>;\n 196→```\n 197→\n 198→**Mapping to plan-ingestion-service**:\n 199→- `status` → `getCurrentVersion()` + `getActiveMeta()`\n 200→- `versions` → `listVersions()`\n 201→- `use` → `setCurrentVersion()`\n 202→- `rollback` → `rollbackVersion()`\n 203→- `validate` → 手动触发校验（通过文件消息）\n 204→\n 205→---\n 206→\n 207→### 5. Document Handler (`src/bot/telegram.js` extension)\n 208→\n 209→**Purpose**: 处理 Telegram 文档消息，识别并保存计划文件。\n 210→\n 211→**Interface**:\n 212→```typescript\n 213→async function handleDocumentUpload(ctx: Context): Promise<void>;\n 214→\n 215→// Logic:\n 216→// 1. Check file extension (.json)\n 217→// 2. Download file content\n 218→// 3. Call validatePlanFile()\n 219→// 4. If valid, call savePlanVersion()\n 220→// 5. Return result with formatted message\n 221→```\n 222→\n 223→---\n 224→\n 225→## Data Models\n 226→\n 227→### PlanStorageConfig\n 228→```typescript\n 229→interface PlanStorageConfig {\n 230→  plansDir: string;           // e.g., \"/project/plans\"\n 231→  featureListDir: string;     // plansDir/feature-list\n 232→  bugFixListDir: string;      // plansDir/bug-fix-list\n 233→  maxVersions: number;        // Optional: limit version count\n 234→  schemaPaths: {\n 235→    featureList: string;      // dev-pipeline/templates/feature-list-schema.json\n 236→    bugFixList: string;       // dev-pipeline/templates/bug-fix-list-schema.json\n 237→  };\n 238→}\n 239→```\n 240→\n 241→### VersionFile\n 242→```json\n 243→{\n 244→  \"version\": \"v20260312-143052\",\n 245→  \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-12T14:30:52Z\",\n 246→  \"uploadedBy\": 12345678,\n 247→  \"itemCount\": 5,\n 248→  \"checksum\": \"sha256:abc123...\"\n 249→}\n 250→```\n 251→\n 252→### CurrentMeta\n 253→```json\n 254→{\n 255→  \"version\": \"v20260312-143052\",\n 256→  \"activatedAt\": \"2026-03-12T14:31:00Z\",\n 257→  \"activatedBy\": 12345678,\n 258→  \"path\": \"/project/plans/feature-list/v20260312-143052.json\"\n 259→}\n 260→```\n 261→\n 262→---\n 263→\n 264→## API Specification\n 265→\n 266→### Plan Ingestion Service API\n 267→\n 268→```typescript\n 269→// Main service export\n 270→export function createPlanIngestionService(config: PlanStorageConfig): PlanIngestionService;\n 271→\n 272→interface PlanIngestionService {\n 273→  // Validation\n 274→  validate(content: string): ValidationResult;\n 275→  \n 276→  // Version management\n 277→  save(type: PlanType, content: string, meta: UploadMeta): Promise<SaveResult>;\n 278→  listVersions(type: PlanType): Promise<VersionInfo[]>;\n 279→  getVersion(type: PlanType, version: string): Promise<string | null>;\n 280→  setCurrent(type: PlanType, version: string): Promise<boolean>;\n 281→  getCurrent(type: PlanType): Promise<ActiveMeta | null>;\n 282→  rollback(type: PlanType): Promise<RollbackResult | null>;\n 283→  \n 284→  // Registry\n 285→  getActivePath(type: PlanType): string;\n 286→}\n 287→```\n 288→\n 289→### Command Handler Integration\n 290→\n 291→```typescript\n 292→// In src/bot/commands/handlers/plan.js\n 293→export const planMeta: CommandMeta = {\n 294→  name: 'plan',\n 295→  aliases: ['p'],\n 296→  subcommands: ['status', 'versions', 'use', 'rollback', 'validate'],\n 297→  requiresAuth: true,\n 298→  helpText: '计划文件管理'\n 299→};\n 300→\n 301→export async function handlePlan(ctx: Context, params: PlanParams): Promise<void>;\n 302→```\n 303→\n 304→---\n 305→\n 306→## Module Dependencies\n 307→\n 308→```\n 309→src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js\n 310→├── src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js (F-001) - paths\n 311→├── dev-pipeline/templates/feature-list-schema.json\n 312→├── dev-pipeline/templates/bug-fix-list-schema.json\n 313→└── npm: ajv (or zod)\n 314→\n 315→src/bot/commands/handlers/plan.js\n 316→├── src/bot/commands/parser.js (F-002)\n 317→├── src/bot/commands/registry.js (F-002)\n 318→├── src/bot/commands/validator.js (F-002)\n 319→├── src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js\n 320→└── src/services/pipeline-control-service.js (F-001)\n 321→\n 322→src/bot/telegram.js (modifications)\n 323→├── src/bot/commands/index.js (F-002)\n 324→├── src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js\n 325→└── telegraf (existing)\n 326→```\n 327→\n 328→---\n 329→\n 330→## Directory Structure\n 331→\n 332→```\n 333→project-root/\n 334→├── plans/                          # New directory for versioned plans\n 335→│   ├── feature-list/\n 336→│   │   ├── v20260312-143052.json\n 337→│   │   ├── v20260312-160321.json\n 338→│   │   └── _current.json          # Meta for current version\n 339→│   └── bug-fix-list/\n 340→│       ├── v20260312-143100.json\n 341→│       └── _current.json\n 342→├── feature-list.json               # Symlink to active version (optional)\n 343→├── bug-fix-list.json               # Symlink to active version (optional)\n 344→├── dev-pipeline/\n 345→│   └── templates/\n 346→│       ├── feature-list-schema.json\n 347→│       └── bug-fix-list-schema.json\n 348→└── src/\n 349→    ├── services/\n 350→    │   └── plan-ingestion-service.js  # New\n 351→    └── bot/\n 352→        ├── telegram.js                # Modify\n 353→        └── commands/\n 354→            └── handlers/\n 355→                └── plan.js             # New\n 356→```\n 357→\n 358→---\n 359→\n 360→## Error Handling\n 361→\n 362→### Error Types\n 363→\n 364→| Code | Message | Example |\n 365→|------|---------|---------|\n 366→| `INVALID_JSON` | JSON 解析失败 | 语法错误 |\n 367→| `UNKNOWN_SCHEMA` | 无法识别的 schema 类型 | 缺少 `$schema` 字段 |\n 368→| `SCHEMA_VALIDATION_FAILED` | Schema 校验失败 | 字段类型错误 |\n 369→| `VERSION_NOT_FOUND` | 版本不存在 | 指定版本号无效 |\n 370→| `NO_PREVIOUS_VERSION` | 没有可回滚的版本 | 仅有一个版本 |\n 371→| `FILE_TOO_LARGE` | 文件过大 | 超过限制 |\n 372→| `SAVE_FAILED` | 保存失败 | 文件系统错误 |\n 373→\n 374→### Error Response Format\n 375→\n 376→```typescript\n 377→interface ValidationErrorDetail {\n 378→  path: string;\n 379→  message: string;\n 380→  example?: string;  // Correct format example\n 381→}\n 382→\n 383→function formatValidationErrors(errors: ValidationError[]): string;\n 384→// Output:\n 385→// ❌ 校验失败:\n 386→// • features[0].id: 缺少必填字段 (示例: \"F-001\")\n 387→// • features[1].priority: 必须为正整数 (当前值: -1)\n 388→```\n 389→\n 390→---\n 391→\n 392→## Test Strategy\n 393→\n 394→### Unit Tests\n 395→\n 396→| Module | Test Cases |\n 397→|--------|------------|\n 398→| `plan-ingestion-service.js` | Schema 校验成功/失败、版本保存/切换/回滚、错误处理 |\n 399→| `handlers/plan.js` | Mock service，验证命令参数解析与调用 |\n 400→\n 401→### Integration Tests\n 402→\n 403→| Scenario | Test |\n 404→|----------|------|\n 405→| 文件上传流程 | 模拟 Telegram document 消息，验证完整保存流程 |\n 406→| 版本切换 | 验证切换后 pipeline 使用正确文件 |\n 407→| 错误隔离 | 验证校验失败不影响当前生效版本 |\n 408→\n 409→### Test Files\n 410→\n 411→```\n 412→tests/services/plan-ingestion-service.test.js\n 413→tests/bot/commands/handlers/plan.test.js\n 414→tests/integration/f003-plan-ingestion.integration.test.js\n 415→```\n 416→\n 417→---\n 418→\n 419→## Risk Assessment\n 420→\n 421→| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |\n 422→|------|------------|--------|------------|\n 423→| Schema 演进不兼容 | Medium | Medium | 版本化 schema，提供迁移指南 |\n 424→| 大文件上传超时 | Low | Medium | 限制文件大小，分块处理 |\n 425→| 版本切换竞态 | Low | High | 使用文件锁或原子操作 |\n 426→| 磁盘空间耗尽 | Low | Medium | 限制最大版本数，定期清理 |\n 427→\n 428→---\n 429→\n 430→## User Story Mapping\n 431→\n 432→| User Story | Components | Tasks |\n 433→|------------|------------|-------|\n 434→| US-1: Upload Plan File | document handler, plan-ingestion-service | T-100, T-101 |\n 435→| US-2: Schema Validation | validator, schema loader | T-010, T-011 |\n 436→| US-3: Version Management | version manager, plan registry | T-012, T-013, T-102, T-103 |\n 437→| US-4: Plan Status Query | status handler, formatter | T-104 |\n 438→| US-5: Plan Integrity | save logic, error handling | T-014, T-105 |\n 439→| US-6: Pipeline Integration | registry, pipeline-control-service | T-015, T-106 |\n 440→\n 441→---\n 442→\n 443→## Integration Points\n 444→\n 445→### With F-001 (Pipeline Infrastructure)\n 446→\n 447→- 复用 `loadPipelineInfraConfig()` 获取路径配置\n 448→- 扩展配置支持 `plansDir` 参数\n 449→- pipeline-control-service 接受动态 `listPath`\n 450→\n 451→### With F-002 (Command Router)\n 452→\n 453→- 复用 `registerCommand()` 注册 `/plan` 命令\n 454→- 复用 `routeCommand()` 处理命令路由\n 455→- 复用 `validator.js` 验证命令参数\n 456→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_885299fbcf5c4e1c9e993fbb","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:29:14.603Z","_requestId":"50df4b32644a4c9c94330fdd421fef57"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"aee90090-9a66-4b52-82d6-00a694dac46b","session_id":"652c262b-723d-40ce-86a3-383fcc2d8e4b","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde5fe93c4aa2965329be96ebedfb","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→/**\n   2→ * Tests for plan-ingestion-service.js\n   3→ * Covers T-010 (schema loader), T-011 (plan validator), T-012 (version manager),\n   4→ * T-013 (plan registry), T-014 (error formatting)\n   5→ */\n   6→import test from 'node:test';\n   7→import assert from 'node:assert/strict';\n   8→import os from 'node:os';\n   9→import path from 'node:path';\n  10→import fs from 'node:fs';\n  11→import { fileURLToPath } from 'node:url';\n  12→\n  13→const __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\n  14→const PROJECT_ROOT = path.resolve(__dirname, '../..');\n  15→\n  16→// We'll import dynamically after setup\n  17→let createPlanIngestionService;\n  18→\n  19→function createTempPlansDir() {\n  20→  const tempDir = fs.mkdtempSync(path.join(os.tmpdir(), 'prizmclaw-plans-'));\n  21→  fs.mkdirSync(path.join(tempDir, 'feature-list'), { recursive: true });\n  22→  fs.mkdirSync(path.join(tempDir, 'bug-fix-list'), { recursive: true });\n  23→  return tempDir;\n  24→}\n  25→\n  26→function createValidFeatureList() {\n  27→  return JSON.stringify({\n  28→    $schema: 'dev-pipeline-feature-list-v1',\n  29→    app_name: 'TestApp',\n  30→    app_description: 'A test application',\n  31→    features: [\n  32→      {\n  33→        id: 'F-001',\n  34→        title: 'Test Feature',\n  35→        description: 'A test feature',\n  36→        priority: 1,\n  37→        dependencies: [],\n  38→        acceptance_criteria: ['AC1: Test passes'],\n  39→        status: 'pending'\n  40→      }\n  41→    ]\n  42→  });\n  43→}\n  44→\n  45→function createValidBugFixList() {\n  46→  return JSON.stringify({\n  47→    $schema: 'dev-pipeline-bug-fix-list-v1',\n  48→    project_name: 'TestProject',\n  49→    bugs: [\n  50→      {\n  51→        id: 'B-001',\n  52→        title: 'Test Bug',\n  53→        description: 'A test bug',\n  54→        severity: 'medium',\n  55→        error_source: { type: 'user_report' },\n  56→        verification_type: 'manual',\n  57→        acceptance_criteria: ['AC1: Bug is fixed'],\n  58→        status: 'pending'\n  59→      }\n  60→    ]\n  61→  });\n  62→}\n  63→\n  64→// ============================================================\n  65→// T-010: Schema Loader Tests\n  66→// ============================================================\n  67→test('T-010: loadSchema should load feature-list schema', async () => {\n  68→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n  69→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ projectRoot: PROJECT_ROOT });\n  70→\n  71→  const schema = service.loadSchema('feature-list');\n  72→  assert.ok(schema);\n  73→  assert.equal(typeof schema, 'object'); // Raw schema object\n  74→});\n  75→\n  76→test('T-010: loadSchema should load bug-fix-list schema', async () => {\n  77→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n  78→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ projectRoot: PROJECT_ROOT });\n  79→\n  80→  const schema = service.loadSchema('bug-fix-list');\n  81→  assert.ok(schema);\n  82→  assert.equal(typeof schema, 'object'); // Raw schema object\n  83→});\n  84→\n  85→test('T-010: loadSchema should throw for unknown schema type', async () => {\n  86→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n  87→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ projectRoot: PROJECT_ROOT });\n  88→\n  89→  assert.throws(\n  90→    () => service.loadSchema('unknown-type'),\n  91→    /unknown.*schema/i\n  92→  );\n  93→});\n  94→\n  95→// ============================================================\n  96→// T-011: Plan Validator Tests\n  97→// ============================================================\n  98→test('T-011: validate should identify feature-list type', async () => {\n  99→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 100→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ projectRoot: PROJECT_ROOT });\n 101→\n 102→  const result = service.validate(createValidFeatureList());\n 103→\n 104→  assert.equal(result.valid, true);\n 105→  assert.equal(result.type, 'feature-list');\n 106→  assert.ok(result.summary);\n 107→  assert.equal(result.summary.name, 'TestApp');\n 108→  assert.equal(result.summary.itemCount, 1);\n 109→});\n 110→\n 111→test('T-011: validate should identify bug-fix-list type', async () => {\n 112→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 113→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ projectRoot: PROJECT_ROOT });\n 114→\n 115→  const result = service.validate(createValidBugFixList());\n 116→\n 117→  assert.equal(result.valid, true);\n 118→  assert.equal(result.type, 'bug-fix-list');\n 119→  assert.ok(result.summary);\n 120→  assert.equal(result.summary.name, 'TestProject');\n 121→  assert.equal(result.summary.itemCount, 1);\n 122→});\n 123→\n 124→test('T-011: validate should return unknown type for missing schema', async () => {\n 125→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 126→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ projectRoot: PROJECT_ROOT });\n 127→\n 128→  const result = service.validate(JSON.stringify({ foo: 'bar' }));\n 129→\n 130→  assert.equal(result.valid, false);\n 131→  assert.equal(result.type, 'unknown');\n 132→});\n 133→\n 134→test('T-011: validate should return field-level errors', async () => {\n 135→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 136→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ projectRoot: PROJECT_ROOT });\n 137→\n 138→  const invalidContent = JSON.stringify({\n 139→    $schema: 'dev-pipeline-feature-list-v1',\n 140→    app_name: 'TestApp',\n 141→    features: [\n 142→      {\n 143→        id: 'INVALID-ID', // Should match F-\\\\d{3}\n 144→        title: 'Test',\n 145→        description: 'Test',\n 146→        priority: -1, // Should be >= 1\n 147→        dependencies: [],\n 148→        acceptance_criteria: [],\n 149→        status: 'invalid-status'\n 150→      }\n 151→    ]\n 152→  });\n 153→\n 154→  const result = service.validate(invalidContent);\n 155→\n 156→  assert.equal(result.valid, false);\n 157→  assert.ok(result.errors.length > 0);\n 158→  // Check that errors have path and message\n 159→  for (const error of result.errors) {\n 160→    assert.ok(error.path, 'Error should have path');\n 161→    assert.ok(error.message, 'Error should have message');\n 162→  }\n 163→});\n 164→\n 165→test('T-011: validate should return status breakdown in summary', async () => {\n 166→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 167→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ projectRoot: PROJECT_ROOT });\n 168→\n 169→  const content = JSON.stringify({\n 170→    $schema: 'dev-pipeline-feature-list-v1',\n 171→    app_name: 'TestApp',\n 172→    features: [\n 173→      { id: 'F-001', title: 'A', description: 'A', priority: 1, dependencies: [], acceptance_criteria: ['AC'], status: 'pending' },\n 174→      { id: 'F-002', title: 'B', description: 'B', priority: 2, dependencies: [], acceptance_criteria: ['AC'], status: 'in_progress' },\n 175→      { id: 'F-003', title: 'C', description: 'C', priority: 3, dependencies: [], acceptance_criteria: ['AC'], status: 'pending' }\n 176→    ]\n 177→  });\n 178→\n 179→  const result = service.validate(content);\n 180→\n 181→  assert.equal(result.valid, true);\n 182→  assert.deepEqual(result.summary.statusBreakdown, { pending: 2, in_progress: 1 });\n 183→});\n 184→\n 185→test('T-011: validate should handle invalid JSON', async () => {\n 186→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 187→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ projectRoot: PROJECT_ROOT });\n 188→\n 189→  const result = service.validate('not valid json');\n 190→\n 191→  assert.equal(result.valid, false);\n 192→  assert.equal(result.type, 'unknown');\n 193→  assert.ok(result.errors.length > 0);\n 194→  assert.match(result.errors[0].message, /json/i);\n 195→});\n 196→\n 197→// ============================================================\n 198→// T-014: Error Formatting Tests\n 199→// ============================================================\n 200→test('T-014: formatValidationErrors should format errors with field paths', async () => {\n 201→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 202→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ projectRoot: PROJECT_ROOT });\n 203→\n 204→  const errors = [\n 205→    { path: 'features[0].id', message: 'Invalid ID format' },\n 206→    { path: 'features[1].priority', message: 'Must be positive' }\n 207→  ];\n 208→\n 209→  const formatted = service.formatValidationErrors(errors);\n 210→\n 211→  assert.match(formatted, /features\\[0\\].id/);\n 212→  assert.match(formatted, /Invalid ID format/);\n 213→  assert.match(formatted, /features\\[1\\].priority/);\n 214→  assert.match(formatted, /Must be positive/);\n 215→});\n 216→\n 217→// ============================================================\n 218→// T-012: Version Manager Tests\n 219→// ============================================================\n 220→test('T-012: save should create versioned file', async () => {\n 221→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 222→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 223→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 224→\n 225→  const result = await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList(), { uploadedBy: 12345 });\n 226→\n 227→  assert.equal(result.success, true);\n 228→  assert.ok(result.version);\n 229→  assert.match(result.version, /^v\\d{8}-\\d{6}$/);\n 230→\n 231→  // Cleanup\n 232→  fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 233→});\n 234→\n 235→test('T-012: listVersions should return version list', async () => {\n 236→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 237→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 238→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 239→\n 240→  // Save two versions\n 241→  await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList(), { uploadedBy: 12345 });\n 242→  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1100)); // Ensure different timestamp\n 243→  await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList(), { uploadedBy: 12345 });\n 244→\n 245→  const versions = await service.listVersions('feature-list');\n 246→\n 247→  assert.equal(versions.length, 2);\n 248→  assert.ok(versions[0].version);\n 249→  assert.ok(versions[0].timestamp);\n 250→  assert.ok(versions[0].itemCount);\n 251→\n 252→  // Cleanup\n 253→  fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 254→});\n 255→\n 256→test('T-012: getVersion should return content', async () => {\n 257→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 258→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 259→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 260→\n 261→  const saved = await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList(), { uploadedBy: 12345 });\n 262→  const content = await service.getVersion('feature-list', saved.version);\n 263→\n 264→  assert.ok(content);\n 265→  const parsed = JSON.parse(content);\n 266→  assert.equal(parsed.app_name, 'TestApp');\n 267→\n 268→  // Cleanup\n 269→  fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 270→});\n 271→\n 272→test('T-012: getVersion should return null for non-existent version', async () => {\n 273→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 274→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 275→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 276→\n 277→  const content = await service.getVersion('feature-list', 'v99999999-999999');\n 278→\n 279→  assert.equal(content, null);\n 280→\n 281→  // Cleanup\n 282→  fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 283→});\n 284→\n 285→// ============================================================\n 286→// T-013: Plan Registry Tests\n 287→// ============================================================\n 288→test('T-013: setCurrent should update _current.json', async () => {\n 289→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 290→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 291→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 292→\n 293→  const saved = await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList(), { uploadedBy: 12345 });\n 294→  const success = await service.setCurrent('feature-list', saved.version);\n 295→\n 296→  assert.equal(success, true);\n 297→\n 298→  const current = await service.getCurrent('feature-list');\n 299→  assert.ok(current);\n 300→  assert.equal(current.version, saved.version);\n 301→\n 302→  // Cleanup\n 303→  fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 304→});\n 305→\n 306→test('T-013: getActivePath should return path to current version', async () => {\n 307→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 308→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 309→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 310→\n 311→  const saved = await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList(), { uploadedBy: 12345 });\n 312→  await service.setCurrent('feature-list', saved.version);\n 313→\n 314→  const activePath = service.getActivePath('feature-list');\n 315→\n 316→  assert.ok(activePath);\n 317→  assert.match(activePath, /feature-list/);\n 318→  assert.match(activePath, new RegExp(saved.version));\n 319→\n 320→  // Cleanup\n 321→  fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 322→});\n 323→\n 324→test('T-013: rollback should switch to previous version', async () => {\n 325→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 326→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 327→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 328→\n 329→  // Save and set first version\n 330→  const v1 = await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList(), { uploadedBy: 12345 });\n 331→  await service.setCurrent('feature-list', v1.version);\n 332→\n 333→  // Save and set second version\n 334→  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1100));\n 335→  const v2 = await service.save('feature-list', JSON.stringify({\n 336→    $schema: 'dev-pipeline-feature-list-v1',\n 337→    app_name: 'TestApp2',\n 338→    features: [\n 339→      { id: 'F-001', title: 'Test', description: 'Test', priority: 1, dependencies: [], acceptance_criteria: ['AC'], status: 'pending' }\n 340→    ]\n 341→  }), { uploadedBy: 12345 });\n 342→  await service.setCurrent('feature-list', v2.version);\n 343→\n 344→  // Rollback\n 345→  const result = await service.rollback('feature-list');\n 346→\n 347→  assert.ok(result);\n 348→  assert.equal(result.previousVersion, v2.version);\n 349→  assert.equal(result.currentVersion, v1.version);\n 350→\n 351→  // Cleanup\n 352→  fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 353→});\n 354→\n 355→test('T-013: rollback should return null when no previous version', async () => {\n 356→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 357→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 358→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 359→\n 360→  // Only one version\n 361→  const v1 = await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList(), { uploadedBy: 12345 });\n 362→  await service.setCurrent('feature-list', v1.version);\n 363→\n 364→  const result = await service.rollback('feature-list');\n 365→\n 366→  assert.equal(result, null);\n 367→\n 368→  // Cleanup\n 369→  fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 370→});\n 371→\n 372→test('T-013: getCurrent should return null when no version set', async () => {\n 373→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 374→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 375→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 376→\n 377→  const current = await service.getCurrent('feature-list');\n 378→\n 379→  assert.equal(current, null);\n 380→\n 381→  // Cleanup\n 382→  fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 383→});\n 384→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_885299fbcf5c4e1c9e993fbb","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:29:14.604Z","_requestId":"50df4b32644a4c9c94330fdd421fef57"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"e4b24dde-bda5-4497-b8c3-d80491309543","session_id":"652c262b-723d-40ce-86a3-383fcc2d8e4b","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde5feb1d17a82c6c889c8dde2322","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→/**\n   2→ * Integration Tests for F-003: Plan Ingestion\n   3→ * Covers file upload flow, version switching, and pipeline integration.\n   4→ */\n   5→import test from 'node:test';\n   6→import assert from 'node:assert/strict';\n   7→import os from 'node:os';\n   8→import path from 'node:path';\n   9→import fs from 'node:fs';\n  10→import { fileURLToPath } from 'node:url';\n  11→\n  12→const __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\n  13→const PROJECT_ROOT = path.resolve(__dirname, '../..');\n  14→\n  15→function createTempPlansDir() {\n  16→  const tempDir = fs.mkdtempSync(path.join(os.tmpdir(), 'prizmclaw-f003-'));\n  17→  fs.mkdirSync(path.join(tempDir, 'feature-list'), { recursive: true });\n  18→  fs.mkdirSync(path.join(tempDir, 'bug-fix-list'), { recursive: true });\n  19→  return tempDir;\n  20→}\n  21→\n  22→function createValidFeatureList(name = 'TestApp') {\n  23→  return JSON.stringify({\n  24→    $schema: 'dev-pipeline-feature-list-v1',\n  25→    app_name: name,\n  26→    features: [\n  27→      {\n  28→        id: 'F-001',\n  29→        title: 'Test Feature',\n  30→        description: 'A test feature',\n  31→        priority: 1,\n  32→        dependencies: [],\n  33→        acceptance_criteria: ['AC1: Test passes'],\n  34→        status: 'pending'\n  35→      }\n  36→    ]\n  37→  });\n  38→}\n  39→\n  40→function createValidBugFixList(name = 'TestProject') {\n  41→  return JSON.stringify({\n  42→    $schema: 'dev-pipeline-bug-fix-list-v1',\n  43→    project_name: name,\n  44→    bugs: [\n  45→      {\n  46→        id: 'B-001',\n  47→        title: 'Test Bug',\n  48→        description: 'A test bug',\n  49→        severity: 'medium',\n  50→        error_source: { type: 'user_report' },\n  51→        verification_type: 'manual',\n  52→        acceptance_criteria: ['AC1: Bug is fixed'],\n  53→        status: 'pending'\n  54→      }\n  55→    ]\n  56→  });\n  57→}\n  58→\n  59→// ============================================================\n  60→// US-1: Upload Plan File Integration Tests\n  61→// ============================================================\n  62→test('US-1: Complete upload flow for feature-list', async () => {\n  63→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n  64→\n  65→  try {\n  66→    const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n  67→    const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n  68→\n  69→    // Simulate upload\n  70→    const content = createValidFeatureList('IntegrationTestApp');\n  71→    const validationResult = service.validate(content);\n  72→\n  73→    assert.equal(validationResult.valid, true, 'Validation should pass');\n  74→    assert.equal(validationResult.type, 'feature-list');\n  75→\n  76→    // Save\n  77→    const saveResult = await service.save('feature-list', content, { uploadedBy: 12345 });\n  78→    assert.equal(saveResult.success, true);\n  79→    assert.ok(saveResult.version);\n  80→\n  81→    // Set as current\n  82→    const setCurrentResult = await service.setCurrent('feature-list', saveResult.version);\n  83→    assert.equal(setCurrentResult, true);\n  84→\n  85→    // Verify content\n  86→    const savedContent = await service.getVersion('feature-list', saveResult.version);\n  87→    assert.ok(savedContent);\n  88→    const parsed = JSON.parse(savedContent);\n  89→    assert.equal(parsed.app_name, 'IntegrationTestApp');\n  90→  } finally {\n  91→    fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n  92→  }\n  93→});\n  94→\n  95→test('US-1: Complete upload flow for bug-fix-list', async () => {\n  96→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n  97→\n  98→  try {\n  99→    const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 100→    const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 101→\n 102→    const content = createValidBugFixList('IntegrationBugProject');\n 103→    const validationResult = service.validate(content);\n 104→\n 105→    assert.equal(validationResult.valid, true);\n 106→    assert.equal(validationResult.type, 'bug-fix-list');\n 107→\n 108→    const saveResult = await service.save('bug-fix-list', content, { uploadedBy: 12345 });\n 109→    assert.equal(saveResult.success, true);\n 110→\n 111→    await service.setCurrent('bug-fix-list', saveResult.version);\n 112→\n 113→    const current = await service.getCurrent('bug-fix-list');\n 114→    assert.equal(current.version, saveResult.version);\n 115→  } finally {\n 116→    fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 117→  }\n 118→});\n 119→\n 120→// ============================================================\n 121→// US-2: Schema Validation Integration Tests\n 122→// ============================================================\n 123→test('US-2: Invalid schema returns field-level errors', async () => {\n 124→  const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 125→  const service = createPlanIngestionService({ projectRoot: PROJECT_ROOT });\n 126→\n 127→  const invalidContent = JSON.stringify({\n 128→    $schema: 'dev-pipeline-feature-list-v1',\n 129→    app_name: 'Test',\n 130→    features: [\n 131→      {\n 132→        id: 'INVALID', // Wrong format\n 133→        title: '', // Empty title\n 134→        description: 'Test',\n 135→        priority: -1, // Negative\n 136→        dependencies: [],\n 137→        acceptance_criteria: [],\n 138→        status: 'invalid-status'\n 139→      }\n 140→    ]\n 141→  });\n 142→\n 143→  const result = service.validate(invalidContent);\n 144→\n 145→  assert.equal(result.valid, false);\n 146→  assert.ok(result.errors.length > 0);\n 147→\n 148→  // Check error formatting\n 149→  const formatted = service.formatValidationErrors(result.errors);\n 150→  assert.ok(formatted.includes('❌'));\n 151→});\n 152→\n 153→test('US-2: Valid file is not saved on validation failure', async () => {\n 154→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 155→\n 156→  try {\n 157→    const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 158→    const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 159→\n 160→    // First save a valid version\n 161→    const validContent = createValidFeatureList('ValidApp');\n 162→    const saveResult = await service.save('feature-list', validContent, { uploadedBy: 123 });\n 163→    await service.setCurrent('feature-list', saveResult.version);\n 164→\n 165→    // Try to save invalid content (should fail validation before save)\n 166→    const invalidContent = JSON.stringify({\n 167→      $schema: 'dev-pipeline-feature-list-v1',\n 168→      // Missing required fields\n 169→    });\n 170→\n 171→    const validationResult = service.validate(invalidContent);\n 172→    assert.equal(validationResult.valid, false);\n 173→\n 174→    // Original version should still be current\n 175→    const current = await service.getCurrent('feature-list');\n 176→    assert.equal(current.version, saveResult.version);\n 177→  } finally {\n 178→    fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 179→  }\n 180→});\n 181→\n 182→// ============================================================\n 183→// US-3: Version Management Integration Tests\n 184→// ============================================================\n 185→test('US-3: Version listing shows all versions', async () => {\n 186→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 187→\n 188→  try {\n 189→    const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 190→    const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 191→\n 192→    // Save multiple versions\n 193→    await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList('App1'), { uploadedBy: 123 });\n 194→    await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1100));\n 195→    await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList('App2'), { uploadedBy: 123 });\n 196→    await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1100));\n 197→    await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList('App3'), { uploadedBy: 123 });\n 198→\n 199→    const versions = await service.listVersions('feature-list');\n 200→\n 201→    assert.equal(versions.length, 3);\n 202→    // Should be sorted by most recent first\n 203→    assert.ok(versions[0].version > versions[1].version);\n 204→  } finally {\n 205→    fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 206→  }\n 207→});\n 208→\n 209→test('US-3: Version switching updates active path', async () => {\n 210→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 211→\n 212→  try {\n 213→    const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 214→    const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 215→\n 216→    // Save two versions\n 217→    const v1 = await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList('App1'), { uploadedBy: 123 });\n 218→    await service.setCurrent('feature-list', v1.version);\n 219→\n 220→    await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1100));\n 221→    const v2 = await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList('App2'), { uploadedBy: 123 });\n 222→    await service.setCurrent('feature-list', v2.version);\n 223→\n 224→    // Active path should be v2\n 225→    let activePath = service.getActivePath('feature-list');\n 226→    assert.ok(activePath.includes(v2.version));\n 227→\n 228→    // Switch to v1\n 229→    await service.setCurrent('feature-list', v1.version);\n 230→\n 231→    activePath = service.getActivePath('feature-list');\n 232→    assert.ok(activePath.includes(v1.version));\n 233→  } finally {\n 234→    fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 235→  }\n 236→});\n 237→\n 238→test('US-3: Rollback switches to previous version', async () => {\n 239→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 240→\n 241→  try {\n 242→    const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 243→    const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 244→\n 245→    const v1 = await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList('App1'), { uploadedBy: 123 });\n 246→    await service.setCurrent('feature-list', v1.version);\n 247→\n 248→    await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1100));\n 249→    const v2 = await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList('App2'), { uploadedBy: 123 });\n 250→    await service.setCurrent('feature-list', v2.version);\n 251→\n 252→    // Rollback\n 253→    const result = await service.rollback('feature-list');\n 254→\n 255→    assert.ok(result);\n 256→    assert.equal(result.previousVersion, v2.version);\n 257→    assert.equal(result.currentVersion, v1.version);\n 258→\n 259→    // Verify current\n 260→    const current = await service.getCurrent('feature-list');\n 261→    assert.equal(current.version, v1.version);\n 262→  } finally {\n 263→    fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 264→  }\n 265→});\n 266→\n 267→// ============================================================\n 268→// US-4: Plan Status Query Integration Tests\n 269→// ============================================================\n 270→test('US-4: Status query returns complete information', async () => {\n 271→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 272→\n 273→  try {\n 274→    const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 275→    const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 276→\n 277→    const content = JSON.stringify({\n 278→      $schema: 'dev-pipeline-feature-list-v1',\n 279→      app_name: 'StatusTestApp',\n 280→      features: [\n 281→        { id: 'F-001', title: 'A', description: 'A', priority: 1, dependencies: [], acceptance_criteria: ['AC'], status: 'pending' },\n 282→        { id: 'F-002', title: 'B', description: 'B', priority: 2, dependencies: [], acceptance_criteria: ['AC'], status: 'in_progress' },\n 283→        { id: 'F-003', title: 'C', description: 'C', priority: 3, dependencies: [], acceptance_criteria: ['AC'], status: 'completed' }\n 284→      ]\n 285→    });\n 286→\n 287→    const saveResult = await service.save('feature-list', content, { uploadedBy: 123 });\n 288→    await service.setCurrent('feature-list', saveResult.version);\n 289→\n 290→    const current = await service.getCurrent('feature-list');\n 291→    const versions = await service.listVersions('feature-list');\n 292→\n 293→    assert.ok(current);\n 294→    assert.equal(current.version, saveResult.version);\n 295→\n 296→    const versionInfo = versions.find(v => v.version === current.version);\n 297→    assert.equal(versionInfo.itemCount, 3);\n 298→  } finally {\n 299→    fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 300→  }\n 301→});\n 302→\n 303→// ============================================================\n 304→// US-6: Pipeline Integration Tests\n 305→// ============================================================\n 306→test('US-6: resolvePlanListPath returns active path', async () => {\n 307→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 308→\n 309→  try {\n 310→    const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 311→    const { resolvePlanListPath } = await import('../../src/services/pipeline-control-service.js');\n 312→\n 313→    const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 314→\n 315→    const saveResult = await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList(), { uploadedBy: 123 });\n 316→    await service.setCurrent('feature-list', saveResult.version);\n 317→\n 318→    const activePath = await resolvePlanListPath({\n 319→      planType: 'feature-list',\n 320→      planService: service\n 321→    });\n 322→\n 323→    assert.ok(activePath);\n 324→    assert.ok(activePath.includes(saveResult.version));\n 325→  } finally {\n 326→    fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 327→  }\n 328→});\n 329→\n 330→test('US-6: resolvePlanListPath with version returns specific path', async () => {\n 331→  const plansDir = createTempPlansDir();\n 332→\n 333→  try {\n 334→    const { createPlanIngestionService } = await import('../../src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js');\n 335→    const { resolvePlanListPath } = await import('../../src/services/pipeline-control-service.js');\n 336→\n 337→    const service = createPlanIngestionService({ plansDir });\n 338→\n 339→    // Save multiple versions\n 340→    await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList('App1'), { uploadedBy: 123 });\n 341→    await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1100));\n 342→    const v2 = await service.save('feature-list', createValidFeatureList('App2'), { uploadedBy: 123 });\n 343→    await service.setCurrent('feature-list', v2.version);\n 344→\n 345→    // Request specific version\n 346→    const specificPath = await resolvePlanListPath({\n 347→      planType: 'feature-list',\n 348→      version: v2.version,\n 349→      planService: service\n 350→    });\n 351→\n 352→    assert.ok(specificPath);\n 353→    assert.ok(specificPath.includes(v2.version));\n 354→  } finally {\n 355→    fs.rmSync(plansDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n 356→  }\n 357→});\n 358→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_885299fbcf5c4e1c9e993fbb","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:29:14.605Z","_requestId":"50df4b32644a4c9c94330fdd421fef57"}
