rrent() |\n\n### US-4: Plan Status Query ✅\n\n| Acceptance Criteria | Status | Evidence |\n|---------------------|--------|----------|\n| 显示当前生效版本信息 | ✅ | `plan.js:138-162` handleStatus() |\n| 显示文件内容摘要 | ✅ | `plan.js:167-184` getStatusForType() |\n\n### US-5: Plan Integrity Protection ✅\n\n| Acceptance Criteria | Status | Evidence |\n|---------------------|--------|----------|\n| 校验失败的文件不覆盖当前生效版本 | ✅ | Validation precedes save in `telegram.js:546-552` |\n| 错误文件保存到隔离目录（可选） | ⚠️ NOT IMPLEMENTED | Spec marks as optional |\n| 保留原有稳定版本可继续执行 | ✅ | `_current.json` only updated on success |\n\n### US-6: Pipeline Integration ✅\n\n| Acceptance Criteria | Status | Evidence |\n|---------------------|--------|----------|\n| 与 pipeline-control-service 集成 | ✅ | `pipeline-control-service.js:25-41` resolvePlanListPath() |\n| 支持动态切换计划文件路径 | ✅ | `getActivePath()` returns current version path |\n| 启动 pipeline 时可指定计划文件版本 | ✅ | `resolvePlanListPath()` accepts version parameter |\n\n---\n\n## Detailed Findings\n\n### HIGH Severity (0)\n\nNone found.\n\n---\n\n### MEDIUM Severity (3)\n\n#### M-01: Test Infrastructure Issue\n- **File**: `tests/services/plan-ingestion-service.test.js`, `tests/integration/f003-plan-ingestion.integration.test.js`\n- **Issue**: Node.js test runner reports \"test run() is being called recursively within a test file\" and skips running tests\n- **Impact**: Tests do not actually execute, providing false confidence in test coverage\n- **Fix**: Refactor test structure to avoid dynamic imports inside test() callbacks, or use a different test organization pattern\n\n#### M-02: Missing Plan Handler Unit Tests\n- **File**: `tests/bot/commands/handlers/handlers.test.js`\n- **Issue**: No unit tests for `handlePlan()` and `planMeta`\n- **Impact**: Command handler logic not covered by unit tests\n- **Fix**: Add tests for plan command handler similar to existing handler tests\n\n#### M-03: Non-Atomic File Write\n- **File**: `src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js:320`\n- **Issue**: `fs.writeFileSync()` is not atomic - partial writes on crash could corrupt files\n- **Impact**: Potential data loss during system crash\n- **Fix**: Write to temporary file then rename atomically:\n```javascript\nconst tempPath = `${versionPath}.tmp`;\nfs.writeFileSync(tempPath, content, 'utf-8');\nfs.renameSync(tempPath, versionPath);\n```\n\n---\n\n### LOW Severity (4)\n\n#### L-01: Plan Interface Naming Differences\n- **File**: `src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js`\n- **Issue**: Function names differ from plan.md specification\n  - Plan: `validatePlanFile()` → Impl: `validate()`\n  - Plan: `savePlanVersion()` → Impl: `save()`\n  - Plan: `getVersionContent()` → Impl: `getVersion()`\n  - Plan: `setCurrentVersion()` → Impl: `setCurrent()`\n  - Plan: `getCurrentVersion()` → Impl: `getCurrent()`\n  - Plan: `rollbackVersion()` → Impl: `rollback()`\n- **Impact**: Minor documentation drift, no functional impact\n- **Recommendation**: Update plan.md to match implementation or add aliases\n\n#### L-02: Missing `refresh()` Method in PlanRegistry\n- **File**: `src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js`\n- **Issue**: plan.md specifies `PlanRegistry.refresh()` method, not implemented\n- **Impact**: No way to invalidate cached state (currently none cached anyway)\n- **Recommendation**: Document as deferred or implement if caching added\n\n#### L-03: Unused `meta.uploadedBy` Parameter\n- **File**: `src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js:302-326`\n- **Issue**: `save()` accepts `meta.uploadedBy` but doesn't store it\n- **Impact**: Loss of audit trail information\n- **Fix**: Store `uploadedBy` in `_current.json` or version metadata\n\n#### L-04: No File Integrity Verification\n- **File**: `src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js`\n- **Issue**: plan.md mentions checksum in VersionFile but not implemented\n- **Impact**: Cannot detect file corruption\n- **Recommendation**: Consider adding SHA256 checksum for integrity verification\n\n---\n\n## Non-Functional Requirements Verification\n\n### NFR-1: Reliability\n| Requirement | Status | Notes |\n|-------------|--------|-------|\n| 文件操作原子性 | ⚠️ | M-03: writeFileSync not atomic |\n| 版本切换幂等性 | ✅ | Verified via setCurrent() logic |\n\n### NFR-2: Performance\n| Requirement | Status | Notes |\n|-------------|--------|-------|\n| 文件上传处理 < 2s | ✅ | Simple JSON parsing, should be fast |\n| Schema 校验 < 500ms (100KB) | ✅ | Ajv is highly optimized |\n| 版本列表查询 < 100ms | ✅ | Simple directory read |\n\n### NFR-3: Usability\n| Requirement | Status | Notes |\n|-------------|--------|-------|\n| 错误信息可读、可操作 | ✅ | formatValidationErrors() provides clear messages |\n| 版本命名直观 | ✅ | v{YYYYMMDD}-{HHMMSS} format |\n| Telegram 消息格式友好 | ✅ | Chinese messages with emoji indicators |\n\n---\n\n## Task Completion Status\n\nAll 18 tasks marked as complete `[x]` in `tasks.md`:\n- Setup Phase: T-001, T-002, T-003 ✅\n- Foundational Phase: T-010, T-011, T-012, T-013, T-014, T-015 ✅\n- User Stories Phase: T-100, T-101, T-102, T-103, T-104, T-105, T-106 ✅\n- Polish Phase: T-901, T-902 ✅\n\n---\n\n## Verdict\n\n# ✅ PASS_WITH_WARNINGS\n\n**Rationale**:\n- All 6 user stories are implemented and meet acceptance criteria\n- No CRITICAL or HIGH severity findings\n- 3 MEDIUM severity findings (test infrastructure, test coverage gap, atomic writes)\n- MEDIUM findings do not block functionality but should be addressed in follow-up\n\n**Required Follow-up Actions**:\n1. **M-01**: Fix test infrastructure to ensure tests actually execute\n2. **M-02**: Add plan handler unit tests\n3. **M-03**: Implement atomic file writes for data integrity\n\n**Optional Improvements**:\n- L-01: Align documentation with implementation\n- L-03: Store `uploadedBy` in metadata\n- L-04: Add file integrity checksums\n\n---\n\n## COMPLETION_SIGNAL\n\n```\nREVIEW_COMPLETE\nFeature: F-003 (feature-and-bug-plan-ingestion)\nPhase: 6 (Code Review)\nVerdict: PASS_WITH_WARNINGS\nFindings: 0 CRITICAL, 0 HIGH, 3 MEDIUM, 4 LOW\nSpec Compliance: 100% (6/6 user stories implemented)\nTask Completion: 100% (18/18 tasks marked complete)\nTest Status: Infrastructure issue prevents actual execution\n```\n\n[Agent ID: agent-e6b6d40d]"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_885299fbcf5c4e1c9e993fbb","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:30:46.389Z","_requestId":"50df4b32644a4c9c94330fdd421fef57"}
